--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages gzip.

The gzip package contains the popular GNU gzip data compression program.
Gzipped files have a .gz extension.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: gzip
       gzip_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: gzip
       gzip_state: 'gzip'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  gzip_state
    Description: Control the state of the role. 'gzip' is a core package and can
                 therefore not be removed.
    Required   : False
    Value      : Predetermined
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'install'
    Options    :
      Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
      Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEPENDENCIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PACKAGES
  gzip
    Version: >= 1.3
    Name   :
      RedHat 6: 'gzip'
      CentOS 6: 'gzip'
      Gentoo 2: 'gzip'

